# SonarQube (self-hosted)

Auth: HTTP Basic with user token as username, empty password.
Base URL via `SONARQUBE_BASE_URL` secret. Token via `SONARQUBE_TOKEN`.

## Endpoints used
- `GET /api/projects/search` — project inventory
- `GET /api/measures/component` — KPI metrics per project
- `GET /api/qualitygates/project_status` — pass/fail
- `GET /api/issues/search` — issue list + facets (severities, types, assignees)
- `GET /api/measures/search_history` — trend charts
- `GET /api/hotspots/search` — security hotspots

## Default metric keys
bugs, vulnerabilities, code_smells, security_hotspots, coverage,
duplicated_lines_density, ncloc, sqale_index (debt minutes),
reliability_rating, security_rating, sqale_rating, alert_status (QG)

## Proxy
`supabase/functions/sonarqube/index.ts` — generic endpoint forwarder.
Client: `src/lib/sonarqube.ts`. Hooks: `src/hooks/useSonarQube.ts`.
